%section#cinema
  .white-background
    .container.content-section
      .row
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2.text-center
          = image_tag('catcinema-program.jpg', class: 'img-responsive', width: "800")
      .row
        .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
          %p.text-center
            Book our cat cinema to enjoy a movie classic with cats or organize your "bring-your-own-movie" event.

